      },
      {
        "text": "Not all liabilities are equal. Short-duration, high-cost liabilities can turn amplification into risk and underperformance. Long-duration, low-cost liabilities can turn amplification into common equity upside. If BTC ARR exceeds the cost of capital, a well-capitalized Bitcoin",
        "url": "https://x.com/saylor/status/2066090698164588560",
        "time": "Sun Jun 14 09:29:43 +0000 2026",
        "likes": 972,
        "retweets": 65
      },
      {
        "text": "The difference between BPS and CEBE BPS is Amplification. With no debt or preferreds, BPS = CEBE BPS and a Bitcoin Treasury Company should track BTC like an ETF. As liabilities increase, BPS and CEBE diverge, creating the potential to outperform BTC.",
        "url": "https://x.com/saylor/status/2066090103982731750",
        "time": "Sun Jun 14 09:27:21 +0000 2026",
        "likes": 681,
        "retweets": 37
      },
      {
        "text": "BPS measures Bitcoin per common share before senior claims. CEBE BPS measures Bitcoin per common share after senior claims. CEBE is the conservative risk metric. BPS is the common equity growth metric. BTC Yield measures BPS execution.",
        "url": "https://x.com/saylor/status/2066069710689444235",
        "time": "Sun Jun 14 08:06:19 +0000 2026",
